                      "Comments": "Silty clay - BK-04; Stewart, L.K., Charlesworth, P.B., Bristow, K.L., Thorburn, P.J., 2006. Estimating deep drainage and nitrate leaching from the root zone under sugarcane using APSIM-SWIM. Agric. Wat. Manage. 81, 315-334.",
                      "Name": "Soil",
                      "ResourceName": null,
                      "Children": [
                        {
                          "$type": "Models.Soils.Physical, Models",
                          "Thickness": [
                            200.0,
